<%= render "shared/header"%>

<header class="w-full bg-home bg-cover h-screen-3/4 lg:h-screen-4/5 bg-center flex justify-center items-center">
  <div class="px-5 py-40 lg:py-52 flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-full">
      <h1 class="font-semibold font-header text-5xl lg:text-8xl lg:px-20 text-center">THE SIMPLE WAY TO BECOME A PILOT</h1>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-xl lg:text-3xl italic text-center py-10">Pilot Training in Phoenix, AZ and Salt Lake City, UT</h2>
      <%= link_to "START FLYING TODAY", root_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row pt-10 pb-0 lg:py-10 bg-white">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2 p-text">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold pb-10 font-header mx-5 text-center">ACCELERATED AIRLINE PROGRAMS</h3>
    <p class="w-3/4">
      With our comprehensive training programs, you
      will gain the skills and knowledge required to
      become a competent pilot and achieve your dream
      of flying commercially.
    </p>
    <p class="w-3/4 py-10">
      Whether you are just starting out or looking to
      advance your career, our Accelerated Airline
      Programs provide a proven path to success in the
      aviation industry. Contact us today to learn more
      and take the first step towards your exciting future
      as a professional pilot.
    </p>
    <%= link_to "CONTACT US", root_path, class: "btn-primary mb-10" %>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2">
    <%=image_tag "airline_pilot_simplifly_alumni.webp", alt: "Simplifly Alumni Pilot Flying for the Airlines", class: "lg:h-screen-2/3"%>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse pt-10 lg:py-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-custom-500 to-cyan-500 text-white">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2 p-text">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold pb-10 font-header mx-5 text-center">ARE YOU READY FOR AN ADVENTURE?</h3>
    <p class="w-3/4">
      At SimpliFly, we believe that aviation is more than
      just a career.  It's an adventure. We offer a range
      of programs that will challenge you, inspire you,
      and give you the opportunity to explore the world
      from a unique perspective.
    </p>
    <p class="w-3/4 py-10">
      Our team of passionate instructors is dedicated to
      sharing their love of aviation and providing a safe
      and enjoyable learning experience for all students.
      So, are you ready for an adventure? Let us help
      you take flight and discover the endless
      possibilities that aviation has to offer.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2">
    <%=image_tag "female_pilot_smiling.webp", alt: "Female pilot smiling", class: "lg:w-1/2"%>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row pt-10 lg:py-10 bg-white">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center lg:w-1/2 p-text">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold pb-10 font-sans mx-5 text-center">BOOK A DISCOVERY FLIGHT</h3>
    <p class="w-3/4 pb-10">
      If you're new to aviation, starting with a Discovery
      Flight is the perfect way to get your feet off the
      ground and experience the joy of flying for the first
      time. During this introductory flight, you'll take the
      controls and work with one of our experienced
      instructors to learn the basics of flying.
    </p>
    <p class="w-3/4 pb-10">
      Our Discovery Flights are the perfect way to
      determine if flying is for you and help you make an
      informed decision about pursuing your pilot's
      license. If you're ready to take the first step, sign
      up for a Discovery Flight today and discover the
      thrill of flying for yourself!
    </p>
    <%= link_to "BOOK A DISCOVERY FLIGHT", root_path, class: "btn-primary mb-10" %>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2">
    <%=image_tag "discovery_flight_cessna.webp", alt: "Taking a discovery flight in a Cessna 172", class: "lg:h-screen-2/3"%>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-center lg:px-10 lg:gap-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-custom-200 lg:pb-10">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/4 lg:hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 p-5 lg:p-0">
    <%= image_tag "team.webp", alt:"Team at Simplifly in an airliner", class: "rounded-t-2xl lg:rounded-none"%>
    <div class="bg-custom-500 text-white font-header font-semibold w-full text-5xl text-center pb-20 rounded-b-2xl lg:rounded-none">
      <%=link_to "OUR TEAM", root_path %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/4 lg:hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 p-5 lg:p-0">
    <%= image_tag "aircraft.webp", alt:"Our Cessna 172 at Simplifly", class: "rounded-t-2xl lg:rounded-none"%>
    <div class="bg-custom-500 text-white font-header font-semibold w-full text-5xl text-center pb-20 rounded-b-2xl lg:rounded-none">
      <%=link_to "AIRCRAFT", root_path %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/4 lg:hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 p-5 lg:p-0">
    <%= image_tag "why_simplifly.webp", alt:"Student at Simplifly passing a checkride!", class: "rounded-t-2xl lg:rounded-none"%>
    <div class="bg-custom-500 text-white font-header font-semibold w-full text-5xl text-center pb-8 rounded-b-2xl lg:rounded-none">
      <%=link_to "WHY SIMPLIFLY?", root_path %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 to-gray-500 text-white">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-20 px-5">
    <h3 class="font-header text-5xl font-semibold text-center">WHAT MAKES SIMPLIFLY DIFFERENT</h3>
    <p class="py-10 text-center max-w-lg text-xl">
      We understand that every student is different, and we believe in
      fostering a supportive learning environment that empowers students to
      reach their full potential. We pride ourselves on providing a unique and
      personalized learning experience that sets us apart from other flight schools.
    </p>
    <%= image_tag "simplifly_scaled.webp"%>
  </div>
</section>


